&lt;p&gt;Seems to be about the same as &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-5298&quot; title=&quot;MalformedObjectNameException in ConnectionMetrics for IPv6 nodes because of &amp;quot;:&amp;quot; characters&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CASSANDRA-5298&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CASSANDRA-5298&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
